org.perfcake.message.sender

Class GroovySender

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.perfcake.message.sender.AbstractSender
      • org.perfcake.message.sender.CommandSender
        • org.perfcake.message.sender.GroovySender
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    MessageSender

    public class GroovySender
extends CommandSender
    Executes an external Groovy script and pass the message payload via the standard input or as a command argument. It extends the CommandSender and executes the groovy script via groovy command with groovy AbstractSender.target passed as an argument.
    Author:
    Martin Večeřa, Pavel Macík
